biography: Tommy is a familiar face at the Hector Trophée, known for his calm demeanor and strategic approach to the game. Representing Espoo Ringside Golf, Tommy brings a level of precision and thoughtfulness to the course that makes him a formidable competitor.

Off the course, Tommy is known for his sportsmanship and camaraderie. While victory at the Hector Trophée and the Victor Trophy has eluded him thus far, his two previous appearances have showcased his dedication and skill. Tommy is eagerly anticipated to make his third appearance in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, where he aims to leverage his experience and tactical acumen to achieve new heights.
